---
title: Fattoush-Inspired Chicken Salad with Spiced Flatbreads and Feta Cheese
description: From our beloved Shawarma Spice Blend to the crispy flatbreads and chickpeas, everything about this salad delights! Our take on this Mediterranean salad is also layered with a roasted garlic dressing, tossed with herbs and fresh veggies and topped with chicken tenders.
